tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE financial_trends (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  revenue DECIMAL,
  expenses DECIMAL,
  profit DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE financial_trends (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  trend_category VARCHAR(50),
  value DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE customer_behavior (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  purchase_date DATE,
  product_name VARCHAR(50),
  purchase_amount DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE historical_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date DATE,
  data_description TEXT,
  source VARCHAR(50)
)
